thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Kris Keevers

author: Kris Keevers
title: Kris Keevers
text: Quick, easy to navigate website once in but had a problem as I changed my account. Phoned up and was fobbed off quickly and told not to go through a particular server. It seemed she was annoyed just to answer my question and couldn't wait to get me off the phone. Otherwise I would have rated 5 stars.
